Summary: Two orange/blue diamonds traveling north to south.
divs: Sighting Detailswhile camping yesterday we were watching fireworks around us,i saw what i thought was maybe a glowing ember crossing the sky from north to south. then as it traveled overhead itmore resembled a diamond with a orange and then blueish reflection from inside the diamond. it traveled behind some trees. at first it seemed not too high but after it passed directly overhead i relized it was really a very high altitude. my girlfriend and i were talking about what it could be, another came across the same place but was smaller, as it passed overhead i relized it was at a higher altitude than the first one. we watched the sky for the rest of the night but did not see anything else.
